## 0. SESSION-START PROTOCOL

1. Verify this AGENTS.md loaded correctly â€” confirm SEJA identifier present
2. Verify MCP connection to `http://localhost:8765/mcp` via health check
3. Load project-local `AGENTS.md` if present at workspace root â€” local overrides
   apply as declared over sections 1, 4, and 5 only
4. If local AGENTS.md not found, trigger project bootstrap workflow
5. Log session start via `seja.telemetry.record_invocation()`

